longBusinessSummary: Brooks Laboratories Limited manufactures and sells pharmaceuticals in India and internationally. The company offers liquid and dry powder injection, carbapenem dry powder injectables, tablets, oral suspension, dry syrup, and eye/ear drops. Brooks Laboratories Limited was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Mumbai, India.
